                            <comment id="13301596" author="lthon" created="Mon, 3 Oct 2016 08:26:41 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;This JIRA is to unify the &lt;em&gt;default&lt;/em&gt; log message format.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The difference would persist if the user changed their log message format in a custom &lt;tt&gt;main&lt;/tt&gt; method, because AFAIK there&apos;s no way to provide custom &lt;tt&gt;logging.properties&lt;/tt&gt;. For that, I filed &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/SWARM-743&quot; title=&quot;allow customizing logging.properties&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SWARM-743&quot;&gt;SWARM-743&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
